        "children": ["w_011", "w_012", "w_013", "w_014", "w_015", "w_016", "w_017", "w_018", "w_019", "w_020", "w_021", "w_022", "w_023", "w_024", "w_025", "w_026", "w_027", "w_028", "w_029", "w_030", "w_031", "w_032", "w_033", "w_034", "w_035", "w_036"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_003",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "我禁止他再喝酒，但他还是喝多了，睡着了。",
        "sentence_index": 3,
        "char_start": 89,
        "char_end": 109,
        "children": ["w_037", "w_038", "w_039", "w_040", "w_041", "w_042", "w_043", "w_044", "w_045", "w_046", "w_047", "w_048", "w_049"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_004",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "我问他有没有钱，他没有，于是我付了账单。",
        "sentence_index": 4,
        "char_start": 109,
        "char_end": 130,
        "children": ["w_050", "w_051", "w_052", "w_053", "w_054", "w_055", "w_056", "w_057", "w_058", "w_059", "w_060", "w_061", "w_062"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_005",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "然后，我叫了一辆车，准备送他回家。",
        "sentence_index": 5,
        "char_start": 130,
        "char_end": 148,
        "children": ["w_063", "w_064", "w_065", "w_066", "w_067", "w_068", "w_069", "w_070", "w_071", "w_072", "w_073"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_006",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "到了他家门口，我按了门铃，然后用他的钥匙打开了门。",
        "sentence_index": 6,
        "char_start": 148,
        "char_end": 176,
        "children": ["w_074", "w_075", "w_076", "w_077", "w_078", "w_079", "w_080", "w_081", "w_082", "w_083", "w_084", "w_085", "w_086", "w_087"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_007",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "他喝醉了吐了一地，我帮他收拾干净，找到了他的钱包、手机和钥匙。",
        "sentence_index": 7,
        "char_start": 176,
        "char_end": 214,
        "children": ["w_088", "w_089", "w_090", "w_091", "w_092", "w_093", "w_094", "w_095", "w_096", "w_097", "w_098", "w_099", "w_100", "w_101", "w_102", "w_103"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_008",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "他的狗看到我们回来了，非常兴奋。",
        "sentence_index": 8,
        "char_start": 214,
        "char_end": 232,
        "children": ["w_104", "w_105", "w_106", "w_107", "w_108", "w_109", "w_110", "w_111", "w_112"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_009",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "我把他扶到床上，他还在说胡话。",
        "sentence_index": 9,
        "char_start": 232,
        "char_end": 250,
        "children": ["w_113", "w_114", "w_115", "w_116", "w_117", "w_118", "w_119", "w_120", "w_121", "w_122"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_010",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "我照顾了他很久，他又吐了一次。",
        "sentence_index": 10,
        "char_start": 250,
        "char_end": 267,
        "children": ["w_123", "w_124", "w_125", "w_126", "w_127", "w_128", "w_129", "w_130", "w_131"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_011",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "看着他熟睡的样子，我感到既无奈又心疼。",
        "sentence_index": 11,
        "char_start": 267,
        "char_end": 291,
        "children": ["w_132", "w_133", "w_134", "w_135", "w_136", "w_137", "w_138", "w_139", "w_140", "w_141", "w_142"]
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "sent_012",
        "unit_type": "sentence",
        "text": "最后，我在他家门口喝了一杯酒，看着天上的月亮，心里想着他什么时候才能好起来。",
        "sentence_index": 12,
        "char_start": 291,
        "char_end": 335,
