        "target_type": "sentence",
        "task_id": "free_translation",
        "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
        "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
        "value": "他喝醉了，开始说胡话，一会儿说他爱的不是那个男人而是我，一会儿又因为失恋哭起来，说自己心都碎了，需要看医生。",
        "confidence": 0.95,
        "llm_used": true,
        "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
        "annotator_note": "将“胡言乱语”口语化为“说胡话”，“心碎了”保留比喻但更顺畅"
      },
      {
        "annotation_id": "ann_sent_003",
        "target_id": "sent_003",
        "target_type": "sentence",
        "task_id": "free_translation",
        "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
        "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
        "value": "我劝他不要再喝了，可他还是喝醉了，直接睡了过去。",
        "confidence": 0.95,
        "llm_used": true,
        "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
        "annotator_note": "“禁止”改为更自然的“劝...不要再喝”，“睡着了”改为“睡了过去”"
      },
      {
        "annotation_id": "ann_sent_004",
        "target_id": "sent_004",
        "target_type": "sentence",
        "task_id": "free_translation",
        "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
        "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
        "value": "我问他身上有没有钱，他说没有，于是我帮忙付了酒钱。",
        "confidence": 0.95,
        "llm_used": true,
        "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
        "annotator_note": "“账单”具体化为“酒钱”，使情境更清晰"
      },
      {
        "annotation_id": "ann_sent_005",
        "target_id": "sent_005",
        "target_type": "sentence",
        "task_id": "free_translation",
        "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
        "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
        "value": "接着，我叫了一辆车，打算把他送回家。",
        "confidence": 0.95,
        "llm_used": true,
        "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
        "annotator_note": "“准备”改为“打算”，表达简洁自然"
      },
      {
        "annotation_id": "ann_sent_006",
        "target_id": "sent_006",
        "target_type": "sentence",
        "task_id": "free_translation",
        "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
        "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
        "value": "到他家门口后，我按了门铃没人应，就用自己的钥匙打开了门。",
        "confidence": 0.95,
        "llm_used": true,
        "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
        "annotator_note": "补充“没人应”使逻辑更连贯，原文描述的是事实序列"
